entry.title: Predict your Kerala Engineering and Medical College based on your KEAM rank.
entry.summary:
The Kerala Engineering and Architecture rank list will be published today at 12:30 PM by the education minister P K Abdu Rabb. The rank list will be available on www.cee.kerala.gov.in

The medical rank list has already been published.
